snippet.description:
❄️🔥 GSG BLIZZARD BATTLEGROUNDS – SEASON 1 | SEMI FINALS (ONLINE) 🔥❄️
🏆 India’s Biggest Winter BGMI Esports Showdown 🏆

The snowstorm has arrived — and only the strongest will survive.

Welcome to the Semi-Finals of Blizzard Battlegrounds Season 1, powered by GSG Esports, where India’s top professional BGMI teams battle it out for dominance, glory, and a ticket to the Grand Finals.

This is not a casual lobby.
This is high-stakes BGMI esports at its absolute peak.

🗓️ SEMI-FINALS SCHEDULE

• Dates: 6th – 8th January 2026
• Match Time: 5:00 PM IST onwards
• Game: Battlegrounds Mobile India (BGMI)
• Mode: Online
• Format: Round Robin
• Total Teams: 24
• Groups: 3 (8 teams each)
• Matches: 18 Total | 12 Matches per Team (4 per day)

🎯 Qualification Rule:
 Top 16 teams qualify for the Grand Finals

🔹 Match 1: Group A 🆚 Group B – Erangel
🔹 Match 2: Group A 🆚 Group C – Miramar
🔹 Match 3: Group B 🆚 Group C – Erangel
🔹 Match 4: Group A 🆚 Group B – Miramar
🔹 Match 5: Group A 🆚 Group C – Erangel
